nodes.text: In 4 BBY,[source?] this human male Imperial officer was sent to retrieve the prisoner Janard from a sinking freighter on the planet Quila. He and several stormtroopers confronted Janard and two rebels, Sabine Wren and Ahsoka Tano, who were attempting to rescue him. In the ensuing fight, Janard punched the officer in the face. Janard was soon shot and killed by one of the stormtroopers.
